1) First Classssd

  i)install nodejs global version(check version in cmd)
  ii)install angular cli globally (use cmd)
  iii) create new folder for angular project( with folder cmd root)
  iii)go to code editer (cmd ---- code .)
  iv) create angular project (ng new projectname)
  v) run your angular server(ng server), if you terminate server(ctrl+c) --localhost:4200/projectname
  vi)create new component like header(projectname>ng generate component header) or (projectname>ng g c header)
  we created four files
  - header.component.html ---you can include html this page
  - header.component.spec.ts (presently not required)
  - header.component.css (individual css)
  - header.component.ts (header component selector, template, css)
  
  above content i learn created new project and component creations 
 

